attributes.description:
This visualization shows the relationship between toss decisions (bat or field) and match outcomes in IPL matches. 
It helps analyze whether choosing to bat or field after winning the toss has a higher probability of winning matches. 
Useful for understanding strategic advantages and decision-making patterns in IPL games.
attributes.title: Toss Decision vs Match Result (Stacked Bar)
